### 2. Get all rides
GET localhost:8080/api/rides

### 3. Get ride by id - {rideId}
GET localhost:8080/api/rides/{rideId}

### 4. update ride status (start ride) - {rideId}
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/rides/start/{rideId}

### 5. delete ride (for some reason) - {rideId}
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/rides/{rideId}

### 6. END RIDE - {rideId}
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/rides/end/{rideId}

### 7. RIDE History/logs (when ride is completed) - {rideId}
GET http://localhost:8080/api/rides/history/{rideId}


